; Coverage test for format.cc lines 610-618
; Test account abbreviation with hierarchical account names.
; The default register format abbreviates long account names to fit
; the column width. This exercises the abbreviation algorithm including
; the weighted adjustment calculation.

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Banking:Checking:Savings:Investments:LongTerm    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg Expenses --columns=90
24-Jan-01 Test                    Ex:Ba:Ch:Sa:Inves:LongTerm         $10.00         $10.00
end test
